<NOTE N="22" PLACE="foot">(22) Dr. Cave's Hi&s;t. Literaria, p. 99.</NOTE> The fourth Council of Carthage in the year 253 was held by 66 Bi&s;hops, concerning the Bapti&s;m of Infants.
